    <item>
      <title>中东问题重回焦点，油价在连跌两日后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东可能再次发生袭击且美国原油库存可能收紧，油价在连续两天下跌后出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 23:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资产支持债券销售额突破 3130 亿美元，创金融危机后纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/asset-backed-sales-top-313-billion-beating-post-gfc-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着银行努力满足新的资本规定，而保险公司对更高收益的债券日益增多，以汽车贷款、飞机租赁、赛百味特许经营费等为抵押的债券销售额已达到金融危机以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/asset-backed-sales-top-313-billion-beating-post-gfc-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 19:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
